    "The following sections will first explore the basic workflows and roles of prompting, and then delve into the specific prompt design strategies employed in this work.",
    "Workflows and RolesIn this study, two different reasoning strategies of the chatbased material design are implemented to optimize AAC formulation.The SFDL is the most basic implementation, consisting of a feedback loop between a user and a Design Assistant (DA) chat model, as shown in Figure 1.",
